    <item>
      <title>Doodle Studio - Art Maker for iOS</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/projects/doodleworld/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/projects/doodleworld/</guid>
      <description>&lt;figure class=&#34;project-image&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;//localhost:1313/projects/doodleworld/doodleworld.gif&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;projects/doodleworld/doodleworld.gif&#34;&#xA;    style=&#34;width:100%; height:auto; display:block; margin:auto;&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;project-image&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;//localhost:1313/projects/doodleworld/ddwc2.jpg&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;projects/doodleworld/ddwc2.jpg&#34;&#xA;    style=&#34;width:100%; height:auto; display:block; margin:auto;&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;project-image-pair&#34; style=&#34;--left-width: 41%; --right-width: 59%;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;project-image-pair-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/projects/doodleworld/ddwc3.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;projects/doodleworld/ddwc3.jpg&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;project-image-pair-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/projects/doodleworld/ddwc1.gif&#34; alt=&#34;projects/doodleworld/ddwc1.gif&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;doodle-studio-for-unity&#34;&gt;Doodle Studio for Unity&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The app is based on a commercial plugin for drawing inside of the Unity 3D editor I released in 2018.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;See: &lt;a href=&#34;https://assetstore.unity.com/packages/tools/painting/doodle-studio-95-108263&#34;&#xA;   target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;Doodle Studio 95! for Unity&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;  &lt;figure class=&#34;project-youtube&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;div class=&#34;project-youtube-frame&#34;&gt;&#xA;      &lt;iframe&#xA;        src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/slDHLcZIXyg&#34;&#xA;        title=&#34;YouTube video&#34;&#xA;        loading=&#34;lazy&#34;&#xA;        allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share&#34;&#xA;        allowfullscreen&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;project-image&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;img&#xA;    src=&#34;//localhost:1313/projects/doodleworld/doodle_window.png&#34;&#xA;    alt=&#34;projects/doodleworld/doodle_window.png&#34;&#xA;    style=&#34;width:100%; height:auto; display:block; margin:auto;&#34;&#xA;  &gt;&#xA;  &#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;figure class=&#34;project-image-pair&#34; style=&#34;--left-width: 50%; --right-width: 50%;&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;project-image-pair-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/projects/doodleworld/doodle_files.png&#34; alt=&#34;projects/doodleworld/doodle_files.png&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&#34;project-image-pair-item&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;      &lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/projects/panoramical/tsath_supercut_hi.gif&#34; alt=&#34;projects/panoramical/tsath_supercut_hi.gif&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;/figure&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Doodle Studio was used in many games, specially on game jams.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A highlight was having one of my favorite game designers Stephen Thecatamites use it to create his award-winnind surrealist horror-comedy series &lt;a href=&#34;https://store.steampowered.com/app/3212530/Anthology_Of_The_Killer/&#34;&#xA;   target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener noreferrer&#34;&gt;Anthology of the Killer&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
