    <item>
      <title>Sidebar</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/_sidebar/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/_sidebar/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m an expert &lt;strong&gt;Creative Technologist&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Technical Artist&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;With 15+ years of experience in Games, XR and Creative Tech, I work on exhibition displays, art installations, videogames and creative software.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I work in Unity, Three.js, WebGPU, and more.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;My work was featured in museums and festivals worldwide (Bozar, SF MoMA, SIGGRAPH) and I collaborated with companies like CTRL-Labs, Google, and Meta on R&amp;amp;D, Realtime Demos and Tools.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m Berlin-based and always open to chat about collaborations and opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
